60218 may have manifested an episode of bright\ngamma-ray emission prior to the burst observed by Swift, in which case GRB\n031203 and XRF 060218 would be \"cosmic twin\" explosions with nearly identical\nhigh-energy properties.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 5 Aug 2009 20:01:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 12 Jan 2010 19:58:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-13"}
